---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout>
  <slot name="head">
    <title>About — The Meridian Residences | Philosophy of Place</title>
    <meta name="description" content="The philosophy, design, and craftsmanship behind The Meridian Residences — where architectural heritage meets contemporary refinement in the heart of South Jakarta." />
  </slot>

  <!-- Hero Mini -->
  <section class="pt-48 pb-24 bg-primary-black">
    <div class="container-standard text-center reveal">
      <p class="overline mb-4">
        <span class="lang-en">About</span>
        <span class="lang-id">Tentang</span>
      </p>
      <h1 class="font-display text-5xl md:text-6xl font-bold text-primary-ivory leading-tight mb-6">
        <span class="lang-en">The Philosophy of Place</span>
        <span class="lang-id">Filosofi Sebuah Tempat</span>
      </h1>
      <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-neutral-300 max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
        <span class="lang-en">Every residence tells a story — of the land it occupies, the hands that shaped it, and the philosophy
        that governed every decision along the way. The Meridian Residences is a proposition built not on square
        metres but on intention.</span>
        <span class="lang-id">Setiap hunian menceritakan sebuah kisah — tentang tanah yang ditempatinya, tangan-tangan yang membentuknya, dan filosofi yang memandu setiap keputusan di sepanjang perjalanannya. The Meridian Residences adalah sebuah proposisi yang dibangun bukan di atas meter persegi, melainkan di atas niat.</span>
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Philosophy Section -->
  <section class="bg-primary-black">
    <div class="container-standard reveal">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        <p class="overline mb-6">
          <span class="lang-en">Our Philosophy</span>
          <span class="lang-id">Filosofi Kami</span>
        </p>
        <h2 class="font-display text-4xl font-bold text-primary-ivory mb-8">
          <span class="lang-en">The Art of Vertical Living</span>
          <span class="lang-id">Seni Kehidupan Vertikal</span>
        </h2>
        <div class="space-y-6 text-lg text-neutral-300 leading-relaxed">
          <p>
            <span class="lang-en">The luxury residence, at its best, is an act of curation. It is not a container for possessions but a
            framework for living — a carefully edited sequence of spaces, materials, and atmospheres that together
            constitute an environment greater than the sum of its parts. The Meridian Residences began with this
            conviction, and every subsequent decision — architectural, material, spatial — has been tested against it.</span>
            <span class="lang-id">Hunian mewah, dalam wujud terbaiknya, adalah sebuah tindakan kurasi. Ia bukan wadah untuk kepemilikan, melainkan kerangka untuk hidup — sebuah rangkaian ruang, material, dan atmosfer yang disusun dengan cermat, yang bersama-sama membentuk sebuah lingkungan yang melampaui jumlah bagian-bagiannya. The Meridian Residences bermula dari keyakinan ini, dan setiap keputusan berikutnya — arsitektural, material, spasial — telah diuji terhadapnya.</span>
          </p>
          <p>
            <span class="lang-en">To curate is to choose. And to choose well, one must first know what to exclude. This is the discipline
            that has shaped The Meridian Residences from its earliest conceptual sketches: not a pursuit of novelty
            for its own sake, but a steady, deliberate process of refining a vision until only the essential remains.</span>
            <span class="lang-id">Mengkurasi berarti memilih. Dan untuk memilih dengan baik, seseorang harus terlebih dahulu tahu apa yang harus dikesampingkan. Inilah disiplin yang membentuk The Meridian Residences sejak sketsa konseptual paling awalnya: bukan pengejaran akan kebaruan semata, melainkan proses yang mantap dan penuh pertimbangan dalam menyempurnakan sebuah visi hingga hanya yang esensial yang tersisa.</span>
          </p>
          <p>
            <span class="lang-en">In a city like Jakarta — where the pace of life at street level can be overwhelming — the residence becomes
            a counterpoint. It is a space of retreat, defined not by what it excludes but by what it has been designed
            to contain: calm, proportion, quality, and light. That, ultimately, is what architecture owes the luxury
            resident. Not a statement. An environment.</span>
            <span class="lang-id">Di kota seperti Jakarta — di mana laju kehidupan di permukaan jalan bisa begitu meluap — hunian menjadi sebuah titik tanding. Ia adalah ruang untuk mundur, yang didefinisikan bukan oleh apa yang dikesampingkannya, melainkan oleh apa yang telah dirancang untuk dikandungnya: ketenangan, proporsi, kualitas, dan cahaya. Itulah, pada akhirnya, yang menjadi hutang arsitektur kepada penghuni mewahnya. Bukan sebuah pernyataan. Sebuah lingkungan.</span>
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Design Philosophy -->
  <section class="bg-primary-black">
    <div class="container-standard reveal">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        <p class="overline mb-6">
          <span class="lang-en">Design Philosophy</span>
          <span class="lang-id">Filosofi Desain</span>
        </p>
        <h2 class="font-display text-4xl font-bold text-primary-ivory mb-8">
          <span class="lang-en">Form Follows Intention</span>
          <span class="lang-id">Bentuk Mengikuti Niat</span>
        </h2>
        <div class="space-y-6 text-lg text-neutral-300 leading-relaxed">
          <p>
            <span class="lang-en">At The Meridian, architecture is understood not as a style but as a discipline — a method of shaping
            experience through space, light, and material. The building's form emerged from a careful reading of its
            site: the orientation of the sun, the prevailing breezes, the long vista across the tree canopy of
            Kebayoran Baru, and the character of the surrounding streetscape — a dignified mix of diplomatic
            residences and mature landscaping.</span>
            <span class="lang-id">Di The Meridian, arsitektur dipahami bukan sebagai gaya, melainkan sebagai disiplin — sebuah metode untuk membentuk pengalaman melalui ruang, cahaya, dan material. Bentuk bangunan ini lahir dari pembacaan yang cermat terhadap tapaknya: orientasi matahari, arah angin yang dominan, pemandangan panjang melintasi kanopi pepohonan Kebayoran Baru, dan karakter lanskap jalan di sekitarnya — perpaduan bermartabat antara kediaman diplomatik dan pertamanan yang matang.</span>
          </p>
          <p>
            <span class="lang-en">The façade speaks a language of quiet authority: bronze-toned vertical fins that create a rhythm of light
            and shadow across the day, a podium that engages the street at a human scale, and an entry sequence that
            reveals itself gradually — rewarding the approach rather than shouting from a distance. Inside, the
            material palette is one of restraint: warm ivories, dark timbers, bronzed metals, and accents of
            champagne gold that appear sparingly and with purpose.</span>
            <span class="lang-id">Fasadnya berbicara dalam bahasa otoritas yang tenang: sirip vertikal bernuansa perunggu yang menciptakan ritme cahaya dan bayangan sepanjang hari, podium yang menyapa jalan dalam skala manusia, dan rangkaian pintu masuk yang terungkap secara bertahap — memberi penghargaan atas setiap langkah mendekat, alih-alih berteriak dari kejauhan. Di dalam, palet materialnya berbicara tentang pengekangan: gading hangat, kayu gelap, logam perunggu, dan aksen emas sampanye yang hadir secara hemat dan penuh tujuan.</span>
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Craftsmanship -->
  <section class="bg-primary-black">
    <div class="container-standard reveal">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        <p class="overline mb-6">
          <span class="lang-en">Craftsmanship</span>
          <span class="lang-id">Keahlian</span>
        </p>
        <h2 class="font-display text-4xl font-bold text-primary-ivory mb-8">
          <span class="lang-en">The Signature of an Unseen Hand</span>
          <span class="lang-id">Tanda Tangan dari Tangan Tak Terlihat</span>
        </h2>
        <div class="space-y-6 text-lg text-neutral-300 leading-relaxed">
          <p>
            <span class="lang-en">Every project of consequence bears, somewhere in its details, the evidence of the people who shaped it.
            At The Meridian Residences, that evidence is in the things most residents will never consciously register:
            the alignment of timber grain across adjacent panels, the precise shadow gap that separates wall from
            floor, the weight and acoustics of a door that closes with a sound best described as a sigh.</span>
            <span class="lang-id">Setiap proyek yang berarti menyimpan, di antara detail-detailnya, jejak dari mereka yang membentuknya. Di The Meridian Residences, jejak itu hadir dalam hal-hal yang mungkin tak akan pernah disadari oleh sebagian besar penghuni: keselarasan serat kayu di antara panel-panel yang berdampingan, celah bayangan presisi yang memisahkan dinding dari lantai, bobot dan akustik sebuah pintu yang menutup dengan suara yang paling tepat digambarkan sebagai sebuah desahan.</span>
          </p>
          <p>
            <span class="lang-en">These are the signatures of craftspeople who have spent decades mastering disciplines that machines cannot
            replicate. The stone mason who selects and positions each marble slab. The joiner who builds cabinetry
            with tolerances measured in fractions of a millimetre. The lighting designer who programs scenes that
            shift imperceptibly across the day, matching the residence's illumination to the circadian rhythm of its
            occupants.</span>
            <span class="lang-id">Inilah tanda tangan para perajin yang telah menghabiskan puluhan tahun menguasai disiplin yang tak dapat ditiru oleh mesin. Pemahat batu yang memilih dan memosisikan setiap lempeng marmer. Tukang kayu yang membangun kabinet dengan toleransi yang diukur dalam pecahan milimeter. Perancang pencahayaan yang memprogram suasana yang bergeser secara tak kasat mata sepanjang hari, menyelaraskan pencahayaan hunian dengan ritme sirkadian para penghuninya.</span>
          </p>
          <p>
            <span class="lang-en">This is not nostalgia for craft in an age of technology. It is the recognition that technology, however
            advanced, is a tool — and that tools produce their finest results when they are guided by hands that have
            learned, through years of practice, what excellence feels like.</span>
            <span class="lang-id">Ini bukanlah nostalgia akan keahlian tangan di era teknologi. Ini adalah pengakuan bahwa teknologi, secanggih apa pun, tetaplah sebuah alat — dan bahwa alat-alat menghasilkan karya terbaiknya ketika dipandu oleh tangan-tangan yang telah belajar, melalui latihan bertahun-tahun, seperti apa rasanya keunggulan itu.</span>
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Timeline -->
  <section class="bg-primary-black">
    <div class="container-standard reveal">
      <p class="overline mb-6">
        <span class="lang-en">The Journey</span>
        <span class="lang-id">Perjalanan</span>
      </p>
      <h2 class="font-display text-4xl font-bold text-primary-ivory mb-12">
        <span class="lang-en">Our Milestones</span>
        <span class="lang-id">Tonggak Kami</span>
      </h2>
      <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        <div class="relative border-l border-gold/20 pl-8 space-y-12">
          <div class="relative">
            <div class="absolute -left-[2.15rem] top-1 w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-gold"></div>
            <p class="text-sm text-gold font-medium mb-2">2019</p>
            <h4 class="font-display text-xl font-semibold text-primary-ivory mb-2">
              <span class="lang-en">Vision Conceived</span>
              <span class="lang-id">Visi Dicanangkan</span>
            </h4>
            <p class="text-neutral-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">
              The concept for The Meridian Residences was born from a conviction that South Jakarta deserved a
              residential offering that would match its growing stature as a global address.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="relative">
            <div class="absolute -left-[2.15rem] top-1 w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-gold"></div>
            <p class="text-sm text-gold font-medium mb-2">2020</p>
            <h4 class="font-display text-xl font-semibold text-primary-ivory mb-2">
              <span class="lang-en">Land Secured</span>
              <span class="lang-id">Lahan Diamankan</span>
            </h4>
            <p class="text-neutral-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">
              A rare parcel in the heart of Kebayoran Baru was identified and acquired — a site of exceptional
              scale and orientation for a development of this calibre.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="relative">
            <div class="absolute -left-[2.15rem] top-1 w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-gold"></div>
            <p class="text-sm text-gold font-medium mb-2">2021</p>
            <h4 class="font-display text-xl font-semibold text-primary-ivory mb-2">
              <span class="lang-en">Design Partnership Formed</span>
              <span class="lang-id">Kemitraan Desain Terbentuk</span>
            </h4>
            <p class="text-neutral-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">
              An international design team was assembled, bringing together architects, interior designers, and
              landscape architects with portfolios spanning the finest residences across Asia Pacific.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="relative">
            <div class="absolute -left-[2.15rem] top-1 w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-gold"></div>
            <p class="text-sm text-gold font-medium mb-2">2023</p>
            <h4 class="font-display text-xl font-semibold text-primary-ivory mb-2">
              <span class="lang-en">Ground Broken</span>
              <span class="lang-id">Peletakan Batu Pertama</span>
            </h4>
            <p class="text-neutral-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">
              Construction commenced on the site, with a commitment to the highest standards of engineering,
              quality control, and craftsmanship at every stage of the build.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="relative">
            <div class="absolute -left-[2.15rem] top-1 w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-gold"></div>
            <p class="text-sm text-gold font-medium mb-2">2024</p>
            <h4 class="font-display text-xl font-semibold text-primary-ivory mb-2">
              <span class="lang-en">Sales Gallery Opened</span>
              <span class="lang-id">Galeri Penjualan Dibuka</span>
            </h4>
            <p class="text-neutral-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">
              The Sales Gallery welcomed its first visitors, offering a curated preview of the residences,
              material selections, and the philosophy that defines The Meridian.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Partnerships -->
  <section class="bg-primary-black">
    <div class="container-standard reveal">
      <p class="overline mb-6">
        <span class="lang-en">Partnerships</span>
        <span class="lang-id">Kemitraan</span>
      </p>
      <h2 class="font-display text-4xl font-bold text-primary-ivory mb-8">
        <span class="lang-en">The Hands That Shape</span>
        <span class="lang-id">Tangan yang Membentuk</span>
      </h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-neutral-300 max-w-2xl mb-12 leading-relaxed">
        The Meridian Residences is the product of an extraordinary collaboration — a convergence of visionaries whose
        individual expertise has been orchestrated into a singular expression of craft.
      </p>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
        <div class="bg-primary-charcoal border border-primary-ivory/5 rounded-sm p-8">
          <p class="text-xs text-gold uppercase tracking-widest mb-6">[ILLUSTRATIVE]</p>
          <h4 class="font-display text-xl font-semibold text-primary-ivory mb-3">Architecture</h4>
          <p class="text-neutral-400 leading-relaxed">
            An internationally recognised architecture practice with a portfolio spanning luxury residential,
            hospitality, and cultural projects across Southeast Asia. Their approach combines contextual sensitivity
            with a commitment to spatial excellence.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-primary-charcoal border border-primary-ivory/5 rounded-sm p-8">
          <p class="text-xs text-gold uppercase tracking-widest mb-6">[ILLUSTRATIVE]</p>
          <h4 class="font-display text-xl font-semibold text-primary-ivory mb-3">Interior Design</h4>
          <p class="text-neutral-400 leading-relaxed">
            A celebrated interior design studio known for creating spaces of quiet luxury — environments where
            every surface, texture, and detail serves the experience of those who inhabit them.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
